        <h2 id="meet-title">Meet <strong>Hannah</strong></h2>
        <p>Hi! I am Hannah! The Owner/Pastry Chef of Honeybear Bake Shop! Ever since I was a young girl, I have wanted to be a pastry chef. I would run home every day from elementary school to watch my favorite show Sweet Dreams with Gale Gand!</p>
        <p>I was inspired by my mother who had her own cookie business when I was young and sold via eBay. She would stay up baking cookies with my Dad into the late hours of the night…</p>
